: Municipio Ituiutaba, Fazenda San [Terejuba], 
<emphasis id="5A1D1015E91D08AE0554850EF3BE61A0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A. Macedo</emphasis>
1807 (MO, RB, SP69893).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
